    <h2 class="parallax"><u><a href=https://www.uiclitlab.com style="color:white">UIC LIT Lab</a></u></h2>
    <p class="parallax_description">I am the director of the UIC LIT Lab. Our mission is to design and develop STEM interest scaffolding in technology-based learning. We specialize in developing learning-companion robots for children to support in-home learning and interest development for science, engineering, and related fields. <br/><br/>For more information about the lab, visit our site at <u><a href=https://www.uiclitlab.com style="color:white">www.uiclitlab.com</a></u></p>
